{"tid":1985383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇絲打試過幾個星期都下面流啡","createTime":"2020-04-23T06:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T07:08:53.000Z","uid":61288,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0fa358e0a15f0ed20b0b0457e2a1820aa6127ba6","tid":1985383,"uid":61288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:18:09.000Z","msg":"我經期一向唔準同亂，最近五年會間中流啡，不過最近呢兩年唔知係咪工作壓力大，一開始流一兩個星期會自動停<br />\n到最近呢兩年每半年就會有一次流足幾個星期都未完，<br />\n<br />\n2018年同2019年尾都因為黎得太長，個陣照過超聲波，冇任何異樣，醫生話係內分泌失調，食左黃體銅就冇事，之後黎正常m，最近呢個月又黎啡，睇左次中醫，食左幾次藥 係少左好多，但開始黎d帶少少淺啡既白帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗緊睇西醫好唔好 但我唔想又食黃體銅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定睇多次中醫好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉d m咁樣 將來點生仔 好驚自己不育 因為好想同依家個男有將來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇絲打有類似經驗 真係覺得好煩同驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75996dc04722678a788c6f5e71c1940ecf7ad72","tid":1985383,"uid":62470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:22:34.000Z","msg":"自己不時都會流啡 但之後都會正常黎月經<br />\n（有時都一個月唔黎咁）<br />\n絲打如果係擔心嘅 去醫生到檢查多次囉！始終醫生係專業 食唔食藥呢啲都係後話啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1415add9657a7c5bd0c2e78cca6bc89bd9df5b1","tid":1985383,"uid":74622,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:22:53.000Z","msg":"去睇醫生啦<br />\n連登問只會答你<br />\n下世小心"},{"pid":"e2910f885d819674762a3eed7dc2c8bc3d8d0d24","tid":1985383,"uid":61288,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a75996dc04722678a788c6f5e71c1940ecf7ad72","tid":1985383,"uid":62470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:22:34.000Z","msg":"自己不時都會流啡 但之後都會正常黎月經<br />\n（有時都一個月唔黎咁）<br />\n絲打如果係擔心嘅 去醫生到檢查多次囉！始終醫生係專業 食唔食藥呢啲都係後話啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:26:02.000Z","msg":"但半年前已經照左超聲波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de49c9e6c4b1dfa93d9009e0e1555bb9ad56b2b8","tid":1985383,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:30:45.000Z","msg":"下世小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6bf119ef5ce7d389e5f192af81f37c86ecbb1b","tid":1985383,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:37:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a87b616c3ef02b08bea5bcaabdc3ebdf6bb9bc3","tid":1985383,"uid":62470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e2910f885d819674762a3eed7dc2c8bc3d8d0d24","tid":1985383,"uid":61288,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a75996dc04722678a788c6f5e71c1940ecf7ad72","tid":1985383,"uid":62470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:22:34.000Z","msg":"自己不時都會流啡 但之後都會正常黎月經<br />\n（有時都一個月唔黎咁）<br />\n絲打如果係擔心嘅 去醫生到檢查多次囉！始終醫生係專業 食唔食藥呢啲都係後話啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:26:02.000Z","msg":"但半年前已經照左超聲波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgm